# This file ensures the bob_sessions/ directory is tracked by git

This directory stores session logs and conversation history from DevLens commands:
- Session transcripts for reference
- Generated report metadata
- Command execution logs

The actual session files are gitignored to avoid committing potentially sensitive
conversation data, but this .gitkeep file ensures the directory structure exists
in the repository.

Session logs can be useful for:
- Debugging command execution
- Understanding what Bob analyzed
- Tracking report generation history
- Reviewing past code reviews